         <section class=" min-h-screen max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4  pt-6 pb-3 ">
            <div id="landing" class=" grid grid-cols-5 md:gap-5 gap-2">
                <div class=" col-span-3 px-5 pt-4 md:pt-7 motion-preset-slide-right-lg motion-duration-2000">
                    <div class="flex flex-col ">
                                    
                        <h1 class=" mb-4 text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl"><p class=" text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r to-emerald-600 from-sky-400 ">Welcome to Lost & Found</p> </h1>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold font-mono mt-2 md:mt-5 text-gray-500 lg:text-2xl dark:text-gray-400 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 ">
                            Lost something important? Don’t worry, it happens! Whether it's your favorite jacket, keys, or even your phone, we're here to help you find it again – fast and easy.
                        </p>
                         <div class="flex md:gap-6 pt-2 md:pt-12">
                            <a href="/register" class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center p-0.5 mb-2 me-2 overflow-hidden text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 rounded-lg group bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-blue-500 group-hover:from-purple-600 group-hover:to-blue-500 hover:text-white dark:text-white focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:focus:ring-blue-800">
                                <span class="relative px-5 py-2.5 transition-all ease-in duration-75 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-md group-hover:bg-opacity-0">
                                    Get Started
                                </span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#about-us" class="text-white bg-color1 hover:bg-gray-500 hover:text-gray-200 hover:cursor-pointer focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-lg px-5 py-3 me-2 mb-2 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-blue-800">About Us</a>
                          
                         </div>

                        </div>
                </div>
                <div class=" col-span-2 motion-preset-pop motion-duration-2000">
                    
                    <img class="h-auto max-w-lg rounded-lg" src="{{ URL('/logo/landing.png') }}" alt="image description">

                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="about-us" class=" pt-3 pb-8">
             
               <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class=" col-span-2 p-3 px-12  ">
                        <h1 class=" text-center mb-2 md:mb-6 font-mono font-bold text-2xl md:text-4xl">Who We Are</h1>
                        <p class=" font-mono text-center font-semibold text-2xl ">We’re a friendly and community-driven platform dedicated to making the process of finding your lost items easier. We know how frustrating it is to lose something important, and we believe everyone deserves a second chance to reconnect with their possessions. That’s why we’ve created a space where anyone can report a lost item or browse through found items, all in one place.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class=" col-span-2 py-4 mb-6 text-center">
                        <button type="button" class="text-white bg-color2 hover:bg-[#4285F4]/90 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-[#4285F4]/50 font-medium rounded-lg text-xl px-5 py-2.5 text-center inline-flex items-center dark:focus:ring-[#4285F4]/55 me-2 mb-2">
                            
                            <span class=" mr-3">Read More</span>

                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class=" h-6 w-7 fill-white " viewBox="0 0 448 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.7.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2025 Fonticons, Inc.--><path d="M438.6 278.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3l-160-160c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3L338.8 224 32 224c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32l306.7 0L233.4 393.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3s32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160z"/></svg>
                            </button>
                    </div>

                  
                <div  class="  p-6 
                 bg-color1 text-white border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-gray-500 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 ">

                    <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white ">Our Mission</h5>
                    <p class=" ">Our goal is simple: To help people find what they’ve lost and return items to their rightful owners. We're all about creating a safe, easy-to-use platform where anyone can help out, whether they’ve found something or lost something themselves.</p>
                </div>
                <div  class="  p-6 bg-color1 text-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-gray-500 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 ">

                    <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white">Join the Community</h5>
                    <p class="font-normal  dark:text-gray-400">We believe in the power of community, and that’s why we’re inviting you to join us. If you’ve found something, share it. If you’ve lost something, report it. Together, we can help make sure fewer things get lost, and more things get found.</p>
